snippet.title: PRINCESS OF THE MOON ~ULTIMATE~ // New Route Added!! FREE Otome Game
snippet.description:
Cyril's route is out today!!

"Princess of the Moon ~Ultimate~" is an otome smartphone game by AbracadabraGames.

GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=info.otomedou.fwe.tsukipuriEn
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/princess-of-the-moon-ultimate/id1413115842?l=ja&ls=1&mt=8

☆ Story ☆
--Welcome, Princess of the Moon

You arrived at a negotiation in a foreign country with remanents of the Middle Ages.
Night has fallen by the time the negotiations end, and you wander into a palace as you follow the moon home......
Suddenly, chosen by the Princess of the Moon
you are to choose the next King that will lead the three kingdoms--!?

Before the fated day, you are to live together with the prince for 3 months,
And take lessons to become a true princess.
Furthermore, you have to perform a secret role to the princes on a night with a full moon...?!

Which prince are you going to choose?

Category/Genre: Romance ADV / Otome
Age Restrictions: for all ages
Price: Free to Play (in-app purchases)
